An all-over confetti-style design covers this attractive shower curtain. The printed design features blue and yellow highlights. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: The confetti shower curtain by Kenneth Cole reaction home was designed exclusively for Bed Bath and Beyond made from 100 percent Indian cotton. The 72 by 72 inch shower curtain features a printed abstract dot pattern in muted blues, grays, greens, and yellows. Also available are coordinating bath mats and towels. The confetti shower curtain is part of the Kenneth Cole reaction home collection. It is available exclusively online and at select Bed Bath and Beyond stores.
